reviews.review_msg: Definitely gives interesting lectures, is quite demanding as a tutorial leader (don't just DO the readings, write notes on them and analyze the information before you come). Exams don't seem difficult but his standards are extremely high. As a straight A student, I struggled to get an A-. But you will NEVER be bored. Great prof.

Very nice and helpful prof, but WHO SAID HE WAS EASY? The midterm and final consisted of memorizing dates after dates and unless you know your material solid, the exams are very tricky. His essay questions on the final killed! Easy to do decently but hard to excel in this class. Also very heavy reading every week.
